Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's my mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First one out.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.31,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we play togeth—
