Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better hurry home.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The days are already getting so short.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the right way?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you fret.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This way's just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.81,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How reassuring.{lol. amazing line}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.29,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Granny, why were you out there in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.61,0:02:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Granny?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my husband!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Youkichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.10,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I cannot thank you enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't quite sure what I'd gotten myself into, to be honest.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs aren't what they used to be, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make it that far into the mountains anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't met her when you did, \NI just don't know what might have happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not have much to offer,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but please, at least rest here before you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it concerns me that she doesn't \Nknow why she ventured out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.34,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the first time. \NShe's been doing it quite a bit lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days, at dusk,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.97,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,usually when there's a beautiful sunset,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll say, "I'm going home," \Nand then she'll try to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that, in rare cases,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people start saying things \Nlike that as they get older.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as though they \Ntemporarily regress to their childhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if not consciously, she may be \Ntrying to return to her childhood home.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she and I are both \Ngetting on in years, to say the least.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that we're \Nstarting to show our age{ in all sorts of ways}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again, \Ntreating me like I've gone senile.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything untrue, did I?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still work much harder than you, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you can't even cook rice on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do without me, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off your high horse already.{lol this couple}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate being called senile so much, \Nthen quit acting like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have company! \NDon't raise your voice in front of our guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're a mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to have one here, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.89,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped us out when our baby had convulsions and when our rice fields became diseased.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure this will make my knee better?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... it {\i1}does{\i0} feel better.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.41,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat it again tomorrow morning, \Nand then it should be completely cured.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrific news.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginko.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Mikage.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.16,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone doesn't remember her past at all,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.23,0:06:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible for her to remember her childhood as she gets older?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say, without knowing more.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife has no memory of her past?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.59,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day a long time ago, \Nshe just suddenly showed up in our village.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.19,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't usually cross my mind anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever I remember that day...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.29,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder what it was all about.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, You.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for my dad to get back from the fields first.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make sure you get home before it gets too dark, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen my daughter, Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkichi, have you seen her?{D:}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us ever saw Akane again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What village are you from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How ominous.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's the child of a demon or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying Akane was eaten by a demon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.81,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, Akane's father volunteered to take her in.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to feel for the poor girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying so hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That new girl never comes and plays with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's no fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better quit pretending to be Akane, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to do this either, you know!{mfw i have no face}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dad gave it to me, so what choice do I have?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}have{\i0} to wear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Mikage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, we accepted Mikage as one of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And after some time,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.02,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,she and I were married.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We raised our children together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We grew old together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.22,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}After spending our lives with each other, \NI was sure that even our bones would be buried together{ in this village}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she started saying, "I'm going home,"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can't be so sure of that anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I must sound crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.00,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that she may remember where she's from one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.40,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If or when she does, I wonder if she'll want to go back there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At dusk, one person vanishes, and another takes his place...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.33,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of this happening before.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sometimes due to an Oomagadoki, or "Great Witching Hour" mushi,{lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which only appears in this world at dusk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who has been engulfed by it
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.46,0:11:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will appear at dusk as a shadow \Nwithout a physical body.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if someone else steps on that shadow or if the shadow steps on them,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.99,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that person will trade places with the shadow's owner, becoming engulfed by the Oomagadoki in exchange.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's the assumption.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.84,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,those who have appeared in such a manner have no memory of their pasts,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which means there's no real proof.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.69,0:12:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying... Akane traded places with Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.84,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what happened to Akane after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way of knowing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.49,0:12:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's possible she traded places with \Nsomeone else in the same way and is living elsewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you figure out where she may have reappeared?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that the Oomagadoki exists in a different world from ours.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can tell when and where \Nour worlds may become connected.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.07,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I hope Akane's found happiness somewhere too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm bored of this game.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play cat's cradle instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we play shadow tag together?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.95,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my knee's all better.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.68,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there are others in the village who have similar problems with their legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could see to them as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.87,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here another night too, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I think I'll take you up on that offer.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.05,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage, I'm going to go catch some fish for Ginko.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't push yourself too hard just because your knee's better.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by evening, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird just came out of my knee!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels a bit better now...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about my husband—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a bruise.{rofl}{hahaha}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a big catch to—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.99,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife! She's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nowhere near sunset, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure she didn't just step out for a bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the lantern too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.93,0:15:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she finally remembered where she's from,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.96,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where... am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no one here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun is always setting here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So lonely...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so lonely here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.33,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet... this is that shadow's fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.23,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all because that shadow stepped on mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we play togeth—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all because that shadow stepped on mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be her?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.17,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.73,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember everything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.17,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were just going to leave without saying anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to go home that badly?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.50,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.33,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Dad and you made me truly happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.24,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't have been me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.40,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sacrificed Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wanted{\i0} to trade places with her,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so I stepped on her shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.40,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I took everything from her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I took Akane from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.01,0:19:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy too, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been happy all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to our home.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some years later,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an epidemic took Mikage's life.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's said that the two lived happily together until she passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it, Akane?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Youkichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.61,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still in that thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.02,0:20:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably couldn't step on someone else's shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.59,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You always were such a gentle, kindhearted girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.66,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I married the girl who stepped on your shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a terrible person?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate her, to this day?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please, just step on my shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane, you have to come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.13,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.11,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.93,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.80,0:22:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.15,0:22:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane's finally come back!
